verifier.value

Interface IValueVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AValueVisitor

    public interface IValueVisitor
    Concrete implementations of this class are visitors to value types. To execute a visitor on a value, pass the visitor instance to the value's "execute" hook method.
